                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/4543: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland (<persName corresp="#p_WHR1"
                            type="from">Wilson</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1932-03-03T13:00:00+01:00"
                            >March 3, 1932—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 3—9:15 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>49. A few minutes before the opening of the Assembly meeting <persName
                        corresp="#p_SN1">Sato</persName> handed me the following message: <pb
                        facs="0601" n="497" xml:id="pg_497"/>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“In view of the retreat of the Chinese forces beyond 20 kilometers to the
                            north of Shanghai the Japanese troops stopped on a line situated at
                            about that distance. The Japanese troops will abstain from all acts of
                            hostilities except those of a strictly defensive nature and will take
                            all measures necessary to the security of inhabitants. The Japanese
                            commanders have made public a declaration to this effect (evening of
                            March 3rd local time).”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_WHR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
